title: La Fuente De Salud Centro Naturista
cleaned_text: - Manuela RI went to look for natural vitamins and omega 3 supplements and they had them and more! This is a very well stocked store. If they don't have it the owner is so sweet and will order it for you. Great customer service and there are also other cool shops in the area. - Tony PI found everything I needed! This store is amazing! Thanks elena!
